data.description: Quiet and private scenic lake view property offers 1980 square feet of living space. 4-bedroom 2 bath triple-wide Manf Home sits on a perm fixed foundation with a 30'x40' detached 2+ car garage/workshop with concrete flooring, electric, and garage. Split bedroom design. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a large separate family room that's perfect for gatherings or quiet nights in. Large deck off the kitchen overlooking the 20+/- stocked lake. Approx. 15/20 minutes +/- from Columbia and minutes from Columbia. 1.41 acres.
